				h1.ar-heading.de-bg.f-oku.wtxt what is DEADEYE's skill?
				.col-md-6
					p.ar-text Expertly trained with long-range and short-range weapons, DEADEYE has superb combat reflexes and pinpoint accuracy. An experienced war veteran, DEADEYE is not above using surveillance devices and explosives to hunt her targets. DEADEYE's skill AIM represents her ability to deal extra damage by hitting her opponent right where it counts.
					p.ar-text So how does Aim work? Your Aim score is represented by a number that begins each turn at 0. Increasing your Aim score provides your Actions and Feats with a temporary damage boost. DEADEYE players can take advantage of this powerful ability by waiting for a big Aim bonus! 
					p.ar-text Included below are a couple of examples on how to use this skill!		
